{
  "stem": "22910.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Here again, we just simply didn't know and did not believe these people came up to, to get us off the wagons because they did say that-- that we should not keep the children in our arms.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But of course, many mothers I'm sure would have gone anyway just to be with their child, not knowing where they're going.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were showered and the shoes we had, the same shoes-- and here again, shoes you cannot start trying on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You cannot walk with shoes which are too small or too big.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So isn't it much easier to let you use your-- keep your shoes?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "With dresses they didn't have to do that, because I got a dress which was up to the floor wide for an old woman.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So what, does that make a difference?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was an older woman who got a cute little dress, short-sleeve, who was an older woman-- not old, no one was old, but an older woman who was much bigger and heavier and so on, so we exchanged.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "With shoes, you cannot do that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was after the shower?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the shower.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We exchanged, so I had a very nice dress, but no panties, no slip, nothing else-- a dress and your own shoes.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So afterwards, people exchanged.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People did all kinds of things because even there we didn't want to-- for one thing, I couldn't have walked in that dress, and she couldn't have put it on.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So afterwards they were marching us towards what turned out to be C Lager in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as we were walking-- first of all, this 'arbei macht frei,' they accomplished a lot by that and the music.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What do you mean?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
